{"ts": "2026-06-07T23:00:37.026079+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "When a user runs the `vidpack` command, they can select from **three encoding profiles** defined in `profiles.toml`:\n\n| Profile | Container | Video Codec | Audio Codec | Key Settings |\n|----------|-----------|-------------|-------------|--------------|\n| **web** | `.mp4` | libx264 (H.264) | AAC | 2 Mbps bitrate, scaled to 1280×720 |\n| **archive** | `.mkv` | libx265 (H.265/HEVC) | FLAC | CRF 18 (constant quality), source resolution |\n| **gif** | `.gif` | *(GIF — palette-based)* | *(none)* | 12 fps, scaled to 480 px wide |\n\n**In short:**\n\n- **`web`** — H.264 in MP4, a lightweight profile optimized for streaming/web delivery.\n- **`archive`** — H.265 in MKV with lossless FLAC audio, a high-quality preservation profile.\n- **`gif`** — A simple animated GIF at 12 fps, suitable for lightweight previews (though the repo notes this single-pass palette generation is a known quality limitation).", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 485, "prompt_tokens": 2752, "total_tokens": 3237, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 218, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 2304, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0002049712, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 6.91712e-05, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.0001358}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780873229-EOy5D83Wonp6vydEHvSQ", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea450-f5ea-7771-87eb-e9b431e2cc17-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2752, "outpu